{"id": 2114, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X领克】人生道路上有哪些对未知的无法预料，经常让你有点点怕？", "description": "人生处处有惊喜，要时刻告诉自己莫慌。", "record_count": 10810, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180110180335IlBkOaRj3WQcNLn4.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-11T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 258816, "content": "不知道自己下一刻会在哪\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235386}, {"id": 259072, "content": "不知道下一秒的天翻地覆会不会改变现在的风平浪静", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236468}, {"id": 258817, "content": "什么时候最爱的人会不爱你", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235389}, {"id": 259073, "content": "每天接受大量的信息，感觉要炸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236471}, {"id": 259586, "content": "千里马常有，伯乐不常有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239451}, {"id": 263939, "content": "害怕他说毕业娶我不是真的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256562}, {"id": 258819, "content": "什么时候才买的起房啊？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089842}, {"id": 258821, "content": "害怕自己在不经意间放弃", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138724}, {"id": 258822, "content": "没斗志", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235400}, {"id": 258823, "content": "不婚的自己不知道是不是真的会孤独终老", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234538}, {"id": 264456, "content": "27～  单身", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258877}, {"id": 258824, "content": "打工不知道哪天会失业", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703179}, {"id": 258825, "content": "哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235407}, {"id": 258826, "content": "时常觉得我需要一份更好的工作来改善生活，不知道什么时候能过上想要的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003604}, {"id": 258827, "content": "每次站上体重秤", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235415}, {"id": 259083, "content": "害怕回过头来不认得曾经的你我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236558}, {"id": 258828, "content": "23了还没有初恋，总觉得以后遇不到一个对的人，更甚者不会恋爱，不会结婚，难道真的要一个人一辈子么", "image": null, "praise_count": 204, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003604}, {"id": 259084, "content": "我要做什么\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236565}, {"id": 258829, "content": "对象？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235023}, {"id": 259085, "content": "死亡和怕无法过上自己想让身边人过的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029392}, {"id": 258830, "content": "难道人这一生就要受苦吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919767}, {"id": 258831, "content": "害怕没赶上这个社会的节凑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047265}, {"id": 258832, "content": "我一直不愿意回家乡。家乡是一个四五线的小城，熟悉，安宁，无压力是它的美好，相反我每次回去都害怕这辈子就这样了，我完全不知道回到家乡我能做些什么，那种对未来毫无憧憬让我害怕。像是吃人的黑洞\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190343}, {"id": 258833, "content": "结婚后的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781817}, {"id": 258835, "content": "害怕不可逆性", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010685}, {"id": 259091, "content": "努力却得不到回报的惶恐快将我淹没", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1135132}, {"id": 258836, "content": "我当前的选择是否正确", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235403}, {"id": 258837, "content": "行业的快速发展 传导在 具体的职业工作上时，那种 不知道  如何优化 工作流程，如何迭代营销模式 的那种迷茫～无所适从", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 9537}, {"id": 259093, "content": "作出的有关未来人生计划存在着自己不可对抗的隐忧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236229}, {"id": 263447, "content": "还不知以后干啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253631}, {"id": 260631, "content": "对未知的恐惧!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242758}, {"id": 258840, "content": "生孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235475}, {"id": 258843, "content": "害怕變得平庸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235506}, {"id": 258844, "content": "长大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212053}, {"id": 258845, "content": "自己所珍惜的东西，在眼前忽然消失。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234059}, {"id": 259613, "content": "生怕现实就是一盆冷水，淋了我这条欢脱的狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239556}, {"id": 258846, "content": "子欲养而亲不待", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 505814}, {"id": 258591, "content": "感情的不确定性太多，让我没什么勇气尝试", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 258592, "content": "不知道这次老师会出哪些题", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 258848, "content": "生活到底为了什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771326}, {"id": 258593, "content": "把自己交给每一个新Tony都会让我害怕死", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 258849, "content": "不得不以舍得的方式来慢慢消磨我舍不得的时光", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235554}, {"id": 258594, "content": "不知道工作中的新挑战是什么样的", "image": null, "praise_count": 178, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 258850, "content": "跟爸爸那边的大部分亲戚闹掰，担心爸爸老了以后如何变对故乡。 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235562}, {"id": 258595, "content": "每一种不得不面对的生计琐事，比如，买车买房", "image": null, "praise_count": 777, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 258851, "content": "下学期见习 没有亲近的人陪着", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235562}, {"id": 258596, "content": "永远不知道什么时候才能过自己想要的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1933, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 258852, "content": "未来对生活的好奇心和新鲜感", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235575}, {"id": 258853, "content": "想着孩子长大，又怕长大了不会再依赖?‍?‍?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235574}, {"id": 258855, "content": "对未知的恐惧\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216497}]}